<div id="c23" class="csc-default">
    <!--  Header: [begin] -->
    <div class="csc-header csc-header-n3"><h1>The texts</h1></div>
    <!--  Header: [end] -->

    <!--  Text: [begin] -->
    <p class="bodytext">The conditions of the Gundert-Portal were to  digitize all Malayalam-, Kannada and Tulu printed texts and manuscripts  which are in the possession of Tübingen university library. They are  mainly part of the Gundert legacy. Some texts, however, may not belong  to the Gundert legacy in a narrow sense but were considered suitable to  be added into this context. Also, there were added printed texts as well  as handwritten notes from Gundert and colleagues in German and English.
    </p>
    <p class="bodytext">All texts which were digitized for the Gundert-Portal will be made accessible under <a href="http://www.uni-tuebingen.de/en/facilities/university-library/searching-borrowing/digitised-collections/digisouthasia.html" title="Opens internal link in new window" target="_blank" class="internal-link-new-window">DigitalSouthAsia / Gundert-Portal</a>. Please note, that the presentaion site is under construction.  </p>
